Name: bypass
Description: Specifies which traffic can bypass the network rules. Possible values are

Name: default_action
Description: The Default Action to use when no rules match from `ip_rules` or `virtual_network_subnet_ids`. Possible values are

Name: ip_rules
Description: One or more IP Addresses, or CIDR Blocks which should be able to access the Key Vault.

Name: virtual_network_subnet_ids
Description: One or more Subnet IDs which should be able to access this Key Vault.
